title: Watch: Cat does killer impression of Jack Nicholson
text:
If you managed to catch Ray Darcy's new Saturday Night Show there the other day, then you would've seen the chap who was holidaying here and managed to get on national tv because he looked like Jack Nicholson.
We know, morto for Ireland etc. That said, this cat has it fairly well down.
Can we expect to see him on Darcy's show in the coming weeks? Fingers crossed.
This cat doing an impression of Jack Nicholson is THE BEST THING. https://t.co/5DzT6rnywF
